<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Land Selection Framework — Prototype</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Spectral:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <link href="https://unpkg.com/maplibre-gl@4.7.1/dist/maplibre-gl.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/maplibre-gl@4.7.1/dist/maplibre-gl.js"></script>

  <style>
    :root {
      --paper: #f6f2eb;
      --paper-2: #efe9df;
      --ink: #1a1a1a;
      --ink-2: #3a3a3a;
      --ink-3: #6b6258;
      --rule: #d8d0c2;
      --accent: #8a3a2a;
      --accent-soft: #c97a5a;
      --map-fade: #1a1a1a;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--paper);
      overflow: hidden;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    #app {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 360px 1fr;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100vw;
    }

    /* === Sidebar === */
    aside {
      background: var(--paper);
      border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 28px 28px 40px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .brand {
      font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }

    .brand em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .sub {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 22px;
    }

    .frame {
      font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--ink-2);
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      padding: 14px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    .frame strong {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      margin: 26px 0 12px;
    }

    /* === Layer list === */
    .layer-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--rule);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    .layer {
      background: var(--paper);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .layer { border-left: 3px solid transparent; transition: background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease; }
    .layer:hover { background: var(--paper-2); }
    .layer.active {
      background: var(--paper-2);
      border-left-color: currentColor;
    }
    .layer.active .swatch { transform: scale(1.0); opacity: 1; }

    .swatch {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-top: 4px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      opacity: 0.45;
      transform: scale(0.85);
      transition: all 0.15s ease;
      background: currentColor;
    }

    .layer-text { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

    .layer-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .layer-meta {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      line-height: 1.4;
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
    }

    .layer-meta span + span::before {
      content: ' · ';
      color: var(--rule);
    }

    .layer.active .layer-name { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

    .layer.pending { opacity: 0.55; }
    .layer.pending .swatch { opacity: 0.25; }
    .layer.pending:hover { background: var(--paper); cursor: default; }
    .layer-note {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      margin-top: 4px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* === Footer / honest-note === */
    .note {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 18px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .credit {
      margin-top: 18px;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    /* === Map === */
    #map {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--paper-2);
    }

    /* Floating value readout */
    .readout {
      position: absolute;
      top: 22px;
      right: 22px;
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      max-width: 280px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 var(--rule), 0 8px 24px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.06);
      z-index: 3;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--ink-2);
      display: none;
    }

    .readout.visible { display: block; animation: readoutIn 0.25s ease; }
    @keyframes readoutIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .map-status {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 22px;
      left: 22px;
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 8px 14px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      z-index: 3;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .readout h3 {
      font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    .readout .val {
      font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 4px 0;
    }

    .readout .src {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding-top: 8px;
      border-top: 1px dotted var(--rule);
    }

    /* Intro overlay */
    .intro {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(246, 242, 235, 0.96);
      z-index: 10;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px;
      transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    }

    .intro.hidden {
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .intro-card {
      max-width: 540px;
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 36px 40px 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.08);
    }

    .intro-card h1 {
      font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 26px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.15;
    }

    .intro-card .label {
      font-size: 10.5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .intro-card p {
      font-family: 'Spectral', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--ink-2);
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .intro-card p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 24px; }

    .intro-card button {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s ease;
    }

    .intro-card button:hover { background: var(--accent); }

    /* MapLibre tweaks */
    .maplibregl-ctrl-attrib { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; }
    .maplibregl-ctrl-bottom-right { padding: 8px; }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      #app { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: auto 1fr; }
      aside { max-height: 40vh; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="app">
    <aside>
      <h1 class="brand">Land Selection Framework <em>— prototype</em></h1>
      <div class="sub">v1 · Europe · sketch build</div>

      <div class="frame">
        Eight criteria for siting a regenerative settlement on a fifty-to-hundred-year horizon. Each layer stands alone — <strong>no scoring, no ranking, no "best places."</strong> The viewer combines them themselves.
      </div>

      <h2>Layers</h2>
      <ul class="layer-list" id="layer-list">
        <!-- populated by JS -->
      </ul>

      <div class="note">
        Every value carries its source and vintage. We never imply more precision than the data supports. Composite "livability" scores are explicitly out of scope.
      </div>

      <div class="credit">
        Working group: Adam · Askja · Deca · Gustaf · Monty<br />
        Documents: r3 (April 2026) · prototype r-sketch (May 2026)
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div id="map">
      <div class="map-status" id="map-status">v1 sketch · click any layer for details</div>
      <div class="readout" id="readout">
        <h3 id="readout-title">—</h3>
        <div class="val" id="readout-value">—</div>
        <div id="readout-desc"></div>
        <div class="src" id="readout-source">—</div>
      </div>

      <div class="intro" id="intro">
        <div class="intro-card">
          <div class="label">Land Selection Framework — v1 sketch</div>
          <h1>A data-honest view of land for the next century.</h1>
          <p>
            Choosing land for a community project meant to outlast a generation is not real-estate shopping. Climate trajectories, water stress, soil resilience, regenerative networks already in place — these decide whether the project still exists in fifty years.
          </p>
          <p>
            This is a sketch of what the full tool will produce. Toggle the layers on the left to read each criterion on its own terms. The data shapes the question; the choice stays with you.
          </p>
          <button id="intro-close">Enter the map</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="module" src="./src/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
